      • hasNext

        public boolean hasNext()
        Similar to 'org.apache.uima.collection.CollectionReader' method hasNext() except interations represents the actual number of documents to be processed, so if the total number of documents in a queue is more than the 'Iterations' value then only the iteration amount will be processed. Multiples of the total available documents will be provided to supplement the list required to meet the total iteration value.
